stopwatch_screen__tabs.name: stopwatch_screen__tabs
stopwatch_screen__tabs.description: A list of tabs for navigating between Alarm, Clock, Timer, and Stopwatch. The Stopwatch tab is currently selected.

stopwatch_screen__more_options_button.name: stopwatch_screen__more_options_button
stopwatch_screen__more_options_button.description: A button in the toolbar for accessing additional options related to the Stopwatch screen.
stopwatch_screen__more_options_button.effect: tap to navigate to the more_options_menu_screen, which displays a popup menu with options for additional settings, including Screen saver, Settings, Send feedback, and Help.

stopwatch_screen__time_display.name: stopwatch_screen__time_display
stopwatch_screen__time_display.description: Displays the current time of the stopwatch, including seconds and hundredths of a second. It is a child of the main stopwatch display.
stopwatch_screen__time_display.effect: The interaction does not change the UI state; the stopwatch_screen remains the same.

stopwatch_screen__time_text.name: stopwatch_screen__time_text
stopwatch_screen__time_text.description: Displays the seconds part of the stopwatch time. It is a child of the stopwatch_screen:time_display element.

stopwatch_screen__hundredths_text.name: stopwatch_screen__hundredths_text
stopwatch_screen__hundredths_text.description: Displays the hundredths of a second part of the stopwatch time. It is a child of the stopwatch_screen:time_display element.

stopwatch_screen__start_button.name: stopwatch_screen__start_button
stopwatch_screen__start_button.description: A button to start the stopwatch. It is located below the time display.

stopwatch_screen__reset_button.name: stopwatch_screen__reset_button
stopwatch_screen__reset_button.description: A button to reset the stopwatch. It is located to the left of the start button.
stopwatch_screen__reset_button.effect: tap to reset the stopwatch time to zero on the stopwatch_screen, which remains the same.

stopwatch_screen__lap_button.name: stopwatch_screen__lap_button
stopwatch_screen__lap_button.description: A button to record a lap time. It is located to the right of the start button.
stopwatch_screen__lap_button.effect: tap to record a lap time on the stopwatch_screen, which remains the same with the lap recorded.

stopwatch_screen__pause_button.name: stopwatch_screen__pause_button
stopwatch_screen__pause_button.description: A button to pause the stopwatch. It is located below the time display.
stopwatch_screen__pause_button.effect: tap to pause the stopwatch, keeping the stopwatch_screen the same with the stopwatch paused.

stopwatch_screen__share_button.name: stopwatch_screen__share_button
stopwatch_screen__share_button.description: A button to share the stopwatch time. It is located to the right of the start button.
